I’m deeply disappointed to share that I was scammed by a Seller/Promoter/Manager/Artist named MUSA DLAMINI @mizzydakoolest  from whom I purchased sneakers earlier this year. Unfortunately, the sneakers I received turned out to be fake, and despite reaching out multiple times since March 2025, Mizzy has refused to issue a refund or take any responsibility.

This has been a frustrating and regrettable experience, and I want to warn others to be extremely cautious if you're considering doing business with him. Based on my experience, Mizzy is not trustworthy and does not stand by the authenticity of his products.

Please be vigilant and share this message to help prevent others from falling victim to the same dishonest behavior.

#ScamAlert #FakeSneakers
